name: Jungle Jump (ewenedmunds)
description:
Survive for as long as you can in this jungle-themed challenge! Leap and bound through oncoming obstacles, while remaining in the bounds of the area, which will slowly shrink over time.

Collect gems to increase your score, and try to survive for as long as possible!

GitHub project: https://github.com/ewenedmunds/leaps-and-bounds
